      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING BERKELEY (5) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at The Gardens over 400m behind Ella Knows (23.49) in a Grade 5. Has ability and is a key runner. MOBILE LAD (7) doesn't win out of turn. Finished in the minors latest when third (20.23) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Has a good record at this journey. Expected to be in this for a long way. JAMAICA RUM (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Scootin' Scooby (19.86) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in this for a long way. LEKTRA BELLA (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
